 in Set. Then we must show that there is a unique group structure on
  E so that h is a homomorphism, and moreover so that h is the
  coequalizer of f and g in Grp.

Since group homomorphisms preserve units, the only choice for unit
  of E is h(e_H). Since split coequalizers are absolute
  coequalizers, the diagram 




